If nothing else clean them up and put a layer of Camellia oil and vacuum pack the tools and keep them with your emergency supplies. In an emergency such as storms, hurricanes etc. when the power goes out and your batteries cannot be recharged and you need to repair something or cover something you will have tools that work.
